source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Drag from one element to another

Usage: bl drag [OPTIONS] <source> <target>

Arguments:
  <source>  CSS selector (or map ref) for the element to drag
  <target>  CSS selector (or map ref) for the drop target

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl drag ".draggable" ".dropzone"
  # Drag element to drop target

  bl drag @e1 @e3
  # Drag using map refs
